Interface BranchCondition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BranchRef, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BranchConditionImpl

    public interface BranchCondition
extends BranchRef
    A representation of the model object 'Branch Condition'. Class for defining branch condition for applying rules

    The following features are supported:

    • Parent
    • Condition Type
    See Also:
